  "instructions": [
    "Prepare anchovy fillets by rinsing gently under cold water to remove any excess salt.",
    "In a bowl, mix flour, cornstarch, ginger, onion, black pepper, and salt until well combined.",
    "Dip anchovy fillets into the spice mixture, ensuring even coating.",
    "Heat a neutral oil in a pan over medium heat (170°C/340°F) until shimmering.",
    "Fry anchovy fillets in batches for 2-3 minutes until golden and crispy.",
    "Remove from oil and drain on paper towels.",
    "Serve immediately for best texture."
